#### HTTP Request

`PUT /api/bindings/{binding_guid}/scheduled_limit_changes/{change_guid}`


#### URI Parameters

Parameter  | Type | Example | Description
---------- | ----------- | ----------- | -----------
binding_guid  | `string` (required) | `540f43bc-b9cc-4126-97a4-a56b64052da4` | GUID of the service binding
change_guid  | `string` (required) | `4ff80e73-5cde-4430-936a-dcbc7f0b7c18` | GUID of the scaling decision
